                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10287" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0639</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">240 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">星河揽才：腾宇科技 AI 招聘的破晓之旅</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Galaxy Talent Acquisition: The Dawn of AI Recruitment at Tengyu Technology</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李涛，王郁蓉，杨祯琪，张茜，张雪瑞，张琪荣</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">腾宇科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字化转型；AI 招聘；智能筛选系统</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Digital transformation; AI recruitment; Intelligent screening system</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例以腾宇科技有限公司（以下简称“腾宇科技”）为研究对象，聚焦于数字化转型背景下科技企业在人才招聘方面遇到的挑战。面对传统招聘模式存在的招聘效率低下、人岗匹配不精准、人才结构断层等问题，腾宇科技通过自主研发的AI智能筛选系统、智能考评系统及元宇宙面试厅等技术手段，并结合胜任力模型、招聘漏斗等理论对招聘模式进行了优化，使其从传统的被动补缺成功转型为主动战略预判，这一转变显著提升了企业的市场竞争优势。通过对本案例的深入学习，能够帮助学生具体地了解AI技术在人才招聘领域的应用方式，以及其对企业核心竞争力所产生的深远影响，为学生在相关领域的学习与实践提供深刻启示和有力借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case study focuses on Tengyu Technology Co., Ltd. (hereinafter referred to as &quot;Tengyu Technology&quot;), examining the challenges faced by technology enterprises in talent recruitment against the backdrop of digital transformation. Confronted with issues such as low recruitment efficiency, inaccurate person-job matching, and talent structure gaps in traditional recruitment models, Tengyu Technology optimized its recruitment approach by integrating independently developed technological tools—including an AI intelligent screening system, an intelligent assessment system, and a metaverse interview hall—with theories like competency models and recruitment funnels. This transformation shifted the company from passive vacancy filling to proactive strategic prediction, significantly enhancing its market competitive advantage. In-depth study of this case will help students gain practical insights into the application of AI technology in talent recruitment and its profound impact on a company&#39;s core competitiveness, providing valuable inspiration and a strong reference for their learning and practice in related fields.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理与开发》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">胜任力模型；三支柱模型；招聘漏斗理论；伦理治理理论；动态能力理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-12</td>
                            </tr>
